{"tid":1187961,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"懷疑自己有ADD","createTime":"2019-06-06T03:27:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-06T06:40:37.000Z","uid":183217,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"a70409b2cccf61801656cddefb1dbcf611501679","tid":1187961,"uid":183217,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T03:27:47.000Z","msg":"唔知自己係咪注專力不足<br />\n<br />\n我好鍾意聽歌 聽新歌可以聽哂成首，但聽住自己嗰playlist 一分鐘就頂唔順要轉歌，但自己好鍾意首歌<br />\n<br />\n睇戲一定要飛住黎睇 如果唔係會熄機<br />\n<br />\n打機一定要開住啲野聽先打到, 例如外國嘅stand up comedy 金田一粵語版 依家就開住brooklyn 99<br />\n<br />\n讀書考試一定要靠提神飲品先溫到 以前中學用葡萄適 依家唔靠monster唔得<br />\n<br />\n小弟其實由細到大都有依啲習慣 但成續keep住冇咩問題所以冇理<br />\n<br />\n但最近發現自己拖延症越黎越嚴重，唔知關唔關ADD事定係自己其實純粹廢柴"},{"pid":"902f686e8e540e1b6a70d2c29232139e13417f97","tid":1187961,"uid":50658,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T03:33:20.000Z","msg":"純粹廢柴"},{"pid":"a27ee0f26606435e5368251810284aa0cef5bdaf","tid":1187961,"uid":13160,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T03:34:10.000Z","msg":"純粹廢柴"},{"pid":"ed306ab407326862336e3303ec119988809684dc","tid":1187961,"uid":170249,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T03:34:41.000Z","msg":"純粹廢柴"},{"pid":"85a828d495de3f8a2bda574a4f18b93da0b680f9","tid":1187961,"uid":222727,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T03:36:17.000Z","msg":"純粹廢柴"},{"pid":"74d47f1bc73fdfc55bcded9b05fc5f154f599f6d","tid":1187961,"uid":73463,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T03:37:37.000Z","msg":"純粹廢柴"},{"pid":"bdb43bfffe407993385aa48a59d16666e1ce98ea","tid":1187961,"uid":180171,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T03:38:19.000Z","msg":"純粹癈柴"},{"pid":"d8a75bbe5235e958914ecef34c61487159f58efb","tid":1187961,"uid":167465,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-06T04:55:07.000Z","msg":"純粹廢柴"},{"pid":"8ce4c518649f406e43671a77c05913d3f220482a","tid":1187961,"uid":72462,"like":1,